    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The Parliament Buildings, completed in 1897, and the Empress Hotel, opened in 1908, are two of Victoria’s most historic landmarks.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria%2C_British_Columbia"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Victoria was the first Canadian city to receive the 2010 Winter Olympics torch, lighting the relay before the Games began.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
