      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria%2C_British_Columbia"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Victoria is the only Canadian provincial capital without a local CBC television station, instead receiving broadcasts from the Vancouver market.",
